Description: Style asset selector modal like Jumper.exchange

Styling Guidelines:
- Modal: Centered, clearly titled, dark background, rounded corners (~20px).
- Search bar at top: Placeholder "Search asset...".
- Scrollable asset list, hover states (gray highlight), rounded corners, spacing (~12px gap).
- Asset entry: Flex layout with icon, token symbol bold, secondary description smaller font.
- Selected asset: Highlight background, checkmark or subtle indicator.
- Coming soon assets: Grayed out, non-clickable.

Functional Logic Preservation:
- Clicking asset updates Zustand state (`setDepositMode`), closes modal.
- Maintain dynamic title context ('send', 'receive', 'deposit').
